{"tid":1387132,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"amazon集運教學","createTime":"2019-07-30T13:01:34.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-25T19:24:46.000Z","uid":184281,"like":93,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":44,"replies":[{"pid":"89a70e7b13e79118ec8ee8b332f2410a14d2f1a6","tid":1387132,"uid":184281,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T13:01:34.000Z","msg":"見而家仲有好多人唔識用集運,  就決定開post 講兩句<br />\n冇信用卡嘅人都唔緊要!!!<br />\n<br />\n1. 注冊一個全新嘅email<br />\n<br />\n2. 去7-11買張tap&amp;go 信用卡<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/D3w2TeG.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FD3w2TeG.png&h=6f02f646&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n3. 注冊amazon account 及 試用 Prime (加快運送速度)<br />\n<br />\n4. 集運物品 (分單唔需要額外收費, 所以1件貨物1張單都唔緊要)<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/EgfWdfr.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FEgfWdfr.png&h=115332da&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n&mdash;&mdash;請自行選擇任何集運公司&mdash;&mdash;<br />\n5. 到貨後, 集運到指定自取點 (記得先付清運費)<br />\n<br />\n6.可以取貨時會收到SMS, 憑SMS 取貨即可<br />\n<br />\n集運喺唔需要本人親身取貨!!!<br />\n所以自己唔得閒嘅話, 記得搵朋友代拎!!!"},{"pid":"f804724f6a207ccc7eef862f1d6595416585423e","tid":1387132,"uid":184281,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T13:10:11.000Z","msg":"覺得有用的話, 就幫手推啦"},{"pid":"d8b41c6d4083e0384975943931f02372d3b7e50a","tid":1387132,"uid":269054,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T13:28:04.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"593ec1a6df93191948bd9264a206db49b71b7a5f","tid":1387132,"uid":25260,"like":33,"dislike":0,"score":33,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T13:30:46.000Z","msg":"講多d啦，step 1-3 唔洗圖都識<br />\n<br />\nstep 4-6 先係重點，有咩集運公司，點集運... 真係唔係人人識"},{"pid":"ca4a75e04ca9c3465d9c3e4d691dbd6610e7cff9","tid":1387132,"uid":560,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"593ec1a6df93191948bd9264a206db49b71b7a5f","tid":1387132,"uid":25260,"like":33,"dislike":0,"score":33,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T13:30:46.000Z","msg":"講多d啦，step 1-3 唔洗圖都識<br />\n<br />\nstep 4-6 先係重點，有咩集運公司，點集運... 真係唔係人人識"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T13:31:03.000Z","msg":"等教學"},{"pid":"811a4aad1630b17caa6f641db9714fe0ba999457","tid":1387132,"uid":31655,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T13:32:51.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"63d174c107074a6e75f20eb3a5654adf93789a7a","tid":1387132,"uid":135201,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T13:39:04.000Z","msg":"運費大約幾多，10個6200 $58.15usd 運費係咪正常？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c1781d53dbf15aa5c554efe6f52b9c4c1525fbed","tid":1387132,"uid":560,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T13:53:19.000Z","msg":"請問點解我揀左 試用 Prime 但最後運費有計錢?"},{"pid":"cdad8efddc129148fec885e6c003784582b416b4","tid":1387132,"uid":45830,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c1781d53dbf15aa5c554efe6f52b9c4c1525fbed","tid":1387132,"uid":560,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T13:53:19.000Z","msg":"請問點解我揀左 試用 Prime 但最後運費有計錢?"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T13:57:58.000Z","msg":"只係快D，同有時候有少少優惠，運費都係要既。"},{"pid":"0ae1bc77946fcb27846c907b6181db36e26e3708","tid":1387132,"uid":184281,"like":8,"dislike":2,"score":6,"quote":{"pid":"593ec1a6df93191948bd9264a206db49b71b7a5f","tid":1387132,"uid":25260,"like":33,"dislike":0,"score":33,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T13:30:46.000Z","msg":"講多d啦，step 1-3 唔洗圖都識<br />\n<br />\nstep 4-6 先係重點，有咩集運公司，點集運... 真係唔係人人識"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T14:04:51.000Z","msg":"詳細教學:<br />\n我自己就用shipbao (貪佢平, 20蚊一磅)<br />\n其他集運公司一樣冇問題<br />\nGOOGLE 一下就好多<br />\n<br />\n4. 係集運公司網頁注冊一個ACCOUNT, 之後就會有個屬於自己嘅地址<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/hFZTfQu.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FhFZTfQu.png&h=c984c192&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n5. 係amazon 買野就係填上面個地址<br />\n<br />\n6. amazon 出貨後, 會有個Tracking ID<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/5kaOPaO.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F5kaOPaO.png&h=1a9afd42&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n7. 需要填返去集運公司網頁 (唔填嘅都可以, 但要收hkd$5)<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/P1z4nvZ.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FP1z4nvZ.png&h=0b787368&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n8. 最後就係集運, 選擇方便朋友拎貨地點即可<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/FU9zKKp.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FFU9zKKp.png&h=863d721c&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"4dd3638becc0ad2914d1007f37192a4ff5448075","tid":1387132,"uid":19217,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T14:04:59.000Z","msg":"1.去集運開個acc 入面有佢us倉地址 通常有幾個倉 有d免稅州 平d但耐些少（e.g. buy and ship/shipbao...）<br />\n2.amazon買野 送去上面地址 amazon本地係免郵<br />\n3.check住集運 佢收到貨會轉status <br />\n4.集埋一齊 揀拎貨方式 自提/ok/7仔 各區都有<br />\n5.等收sms 去到憑code俾錢拎貨 唔會理你邊個<br />\n<br />\n同常一磅廿零蚊度 平直運一半度 但就耐d"},{"pid":"a38a35bf9920d4498e327d283b5ad325e13f9f75","tid":1387132,"uid":184281,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c1781d53dbf15aa5c554efe6f52b9c4c1525fbed","tid":1387132,"uid":560,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T13:53:19.000Z","msg":"請問點解我揀左 試用 Prime 但最後運費有計錢?"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T14:08:06.000Z","msg":"Prime 只for 美國, 通常1-2日就到美國集運倉, 到集運倉後,1星期到香港<br />\n直寄香港有冇Prime都冇影響, 但會貴好多"},{"pid":"5ba110fe3326e3ac6c9aa55ce006b18f8f130843","tid":1387132,"uid":156890,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T14:08:36.000Z","msg":"有用留名"},{"pid":"7f2c74d8a6e43945d96a512804c4397f973f130d","tid":1387132,"uid":184281,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"63d174c107074a6e75f20eb3a5654adf93789a7a","tid":1387132,"uid":135201,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T13:39:04.000Z","msg":"運費大約幾多，10個6200 $58.15usd 運費係咪正常？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T14:09:08