<br />\n6.可以取貨時會收到SMS, 憑SMS 取貨即可<br />\n<br />\n集運喺唔需要本人親身取貨!!!<br />\n所以自己唔得閒嘅話, 記得搵朋友代拎!!!"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-01T06:22:41.000Z","msg":"認真講句，要集運都唔好搵中資公司"},{"pid":"8d1eb3435b3003322d81f1a313edb88e6f1c41fe","tid":1387132,"uid":263367,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-01T06:22:55.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"38ff4517d84240db68a56a8efe467c358f4d4c9d","tid":1387132,"uid":203547,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e7b34c4aef18c15d3a95e88a0925f45282460817","tid":1387132,"uid":203547,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-08-01T06:06:57.000Z","msg":"請問申報果陣，口罩可以就咁直接寫口罩？"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-08-01T06:27:28.000Z","msg":"請問有冇巴打答到我？我訂緊貨"},{"pid":"478d69af9f7e43df87650e51e3684d758c6a8b0d","tid":1387132,"uid":109840,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"5e6c2066a2a4c4a938fe426a89b8a143fd238fb8","tid":1387132,"uid":30976,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-31T08:39:02.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-01T06:56:01.000Z","msg":"我都用開buyandship<br />\n但係佢用locker/circle k嘅話比運費方法得信用卡<br />\n如果現金比就要去自提點取件或者上門送貨服務<br />\n會唔會危險？"},{"pid":"5894b52920a342baffe0e6985436eab713c3bf37","tid":1387132,"uid":260493,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-01T09:03:22.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b139df6f2a33ccb526b9c187a97d8cadab3d7cbf","tid":1387132,"uid":261796,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-01T09:06:46.000Z","msg":"點解唔用Amazon 個送貨？"},{"pid":"ab2241385105cd8ed30120dcefd2b57656516499","tid":1387132,"uid":261796,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-01T09:08:35.000Z","msg":"Btw Amazon 有D唔可以送過黎香港，又係唔係可以用集運解決？"},{"pid":"753c7cee4c71783b32e022b25b92fb7f6f85644b","tid":1387132,"uid":68598,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-01T09:11:13.00